ssess your transversal competences.\n2\ufe0f\u20e3 Improve your communication and public speaking skills.\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Defend a commercial speech.\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Speed up decision making.\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Promote teamwork.\n\nIdeal for professionals looking to improve their interpersonal skills in an immersive, interactive and effective way!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "SoftSkills_Logo_8100x1296px.png", "id": "1158856758691457", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974786_1158856762024790_8351105602424236604_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=093KI4b4LIQQ7kNvgH2OsoU&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBoePxLPcCSxW36wKmWPI266XvOYDvb98ccxjOs9UFzSw&oe=67446269"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-portrait_1008x1440px.png", "id": "1001238441075007", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031591_1001238447741673_2783185145492224256_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=sMZQu-smq2QQ7kNvgEfudxw&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCbDdNUsl8-i4uYTnNBZ1nRS4AUMHlembUFCvKf3cMPsg&oe=67447B2F"}, {"file_name": "INVELON_Icon-512x512px.png", "id": "837105901661785", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476759_837105904995118_1711704673161247418_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qpAHzisfEmgQ7kNvgGD0G40&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAVsb7lRekVG0cXEKZWCauSw2HLpft78iGrmAkaQ2rfBA&oe=67447073"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Hero-cover_3000x900px.png", "id": "436545955954692", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974777_436545959288025_6494250809818469750_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1hYythuq87oQ7kNvgEA3V3z&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBn24RmRyPM2aMFo3UF8mwBlcSVMFBLR4dnqKynSfz4gA&oe=67445845"}, {"file_name